    dc:description "Fig. 4.Ero lizae sp. nov., paratype, ♀ (NHMUK 015134292). A–D. Habitus. A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view. C. Ventral view. D. Posterior view. E. Epigyne, cleared, ventral view. F. Vulva, cleared, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–D = 1 mm; E–F = 0.5 mm." ;
