<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10613428>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Ero lizae sp. nov., additional illustrations of female genitalia. A, E, G. Paratype (BE_RMCA_ ARA.Ara.133370). B–D, F, H. Paratype (BE_RMCA_ARA-Ara.133384). A. Epigyne, ventral view, slightly posterior. B. Idem, ventral view. C. Idem, slightly anterior. D. Idem, anterior view. E. Vulva, ventral view. F. Idem. G. Idem, slightly lateral. H. Idem, slightly anterior. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
